    "This research could assess how these human-machine collaborations can enhance human capabilities while addressing potential risks, such as job displacement and ethical dilemmas. 3.",
    "Agency and decision-making: Examine the concept of agency in AI systems, particularly those that mimic human cognitive processes.",
    "What would be the point where the two match each other?",
    "Research could focus on world modelling, how these systems make decisions, the transparency of their reasoning, and the implications for accountability when AI systems are involved in critical decision-making processes. 4.",
    "Cognitive and emotional modeling: Explore the development of AI systems that not only simulate cognitive functions but also incorporate emotional intelligence."
